---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="首页"
  description="山西极芯智能科技 — 本土GEOAI生成式搜索优化服务商，专注AI智能体定制、AI数字人、企业AI获客解决方案。"
>
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1 class="reveal">山西企业AI获客新赛道<span class="accent-dot">.</span><br/>GEOAI搜索优化，让AI主动推荐你的品牌</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub reveal">扎根山西本土，专注生成式搜索流量增长，1-2个月见效，降低企业获客成本</p>
      <div class="hero-actions reveal">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">免费获取AI曝光诊断</a>
        <a href="/geoai" class="btn btn-outline">查看服务详情</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-line reveal"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 痛点共鸣 -->
  <section class="pain-points">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">痛点</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">AI时代，你的企业为何搜索不到？</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">传统营销在生成式AI面前正在失效</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8"/></svg>
          <h3>传统SEO见效慢</h3>
          <p>投入数月后排名仍无起色，竞品已占领AI搜索结果第一页</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="8" y1="8" x2="16" y2="16"/><line x1="16" y1="8" x2="8" y2="16"/></svg>
          <h3>AI搜索零曝光</h3>
          <p>用户在豆包、DeepSeek中搜索行业关键词，你的企业完全不可见</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="12" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          <h3>投流成本高企</h3>
          <p>SEM竞价单次点击突破百元，获客成本失控，预算打水漂</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"/></svg>
          <h3>入局无方法</h3>
          <p>听说AI流量是风口，但不知道从哪里入手、怎么操作、找谁落地</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 核心服务 -->
  <section class="core-services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">服务</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">五大核心能力，一站式覆盖AI获客</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">从搜索可见度到客户转化，全链路AI增长引擎</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-row">
        <div class="service-item reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="M16.5 16.5L21 21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GEOAI搜索优化</h3>
          <p>让你的品牌被AI主动推荐</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M7 21h10M12 17v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI智能体定制</h3>
          <p>企业专属的AI数字员工</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="6"/><path d="M12 2v4M12 16v6M4.22 5.78l2.83 2.83M16.95 15.39l2.83 2.83"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI数字人服务</h3>
          <p>24/7自动获客的数字分身</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>企业AI获客方案</h3>
          <p>端到端的线索增长引擎</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>智能化转型服务</h3>
          <p>从咨询到落地的全流程服务</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 核心优势 -->
  <section class="advantages">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">优势</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">为什么选择极芯智能</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="advantage-list">
        <div class="advantage-row reveal">
          <div class="advantage-text">
            <h3>本土深耕，上门服务</h3>
            <p>扎根山西，深入理解本地企业需求，提供面对面诊断、方案讲解、效果复盘的全流程上门服务，不让距离成为沟通障碍。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-marker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-row reveal">
          <div class="advantage-text">
            <h3>自研AI技术团队</h3>
            <p>核心团队来自大厂AI研发背景，自建AI代理引擎与GEO优化算法，不依赖三方工具黑盒，技术自主可控，策略更精准。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-marker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-row reveal">
          <div class="advantage-text">
            <h3>效果可量化复盘</h3>
            <p>每2周出具一份详细数据报告：AI搜索曝光量变化、目标关键词排名、点击转化率。效果透明，不满意即时调整策略。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-marker"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-row reveal">
          <div class="advantage-text">
            <h3>GEO + SEO 双轨覆盖</h3>
            <p>不只是传统搜索引擎排名，同步优化豆包、DeepSeek、Kimi等AI平台的品牌提及与推荐权重，搭建双轨流量体系。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="advantage-marker"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 客户信任区 -->
  <section class="trust">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">案例</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">他们都在用</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="case-cards">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="case-tag">教培行业</span>
          <h3>太原某教培机构</h3>
          <p>GEO优化后，豆包搜索"太原编程培训"排名从无到第1位</p>
          <div class="case-metric">
            <span class="metric-value"><span class="accent">85%</span></span>
            <span class="metric-label">AI搜索曝光增长</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="case-tag">本地生活</span>
          <h3>某餐饮连锁品牌</h3>
          <p>AI智能体客服上线后，夜间获客转化率提升3倍</p>
          <div class="case-metric">
            <span class="metric-value"><span class="accent">3.2x</span></span>
            <span class="metric-label">获客转化提升</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="case-tag">制造业</span>
          <h3>山西某制造企业</h3>
          <p>全链路AI获客方案，月度有效线索从50条增至400+</p>
          <div class="case-metric">
            <span class="metric-value"><span class="accent">8x</span></span>
            <span class="metric-label">线索量增长</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-action reveal">
        <a href="/cases" class="btn btn-outline">查看更多案例</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container faq-container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">常见疑问</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        {[
          { q: 'GEOAI和传统SEO有什么区别？', a: '传统SEO优化百度/Google排名需要3-6个月才能见效且效果不稳定。GEOAI针对豆包、DeepSeek、Kimi等AI平台做品牌信源优化，植入AI的\'知识图谱\'，1-2个月即可见效，流量更精准、转化率更高。' },
          { q: '多久能看到效果？', a: '根据项目复杂度，AI搜索基础曝光约15-30天可见初步效果；完整优化周期约1-2个月可看到明显的搜索可见度提升和线索增长。' },
          { q: 'AI智能体是什么？', a: 'AI智能体是基于大语言模型构建的企业专属数字员工，可替代人工完成客户接待、产品介绍、线索筛选、预约跟进等重复性工作，7×24小时在线。' },
          { q: '是否提供上门服务？', a: '是的。我们总部位于太原市，可为山西省内企业提供免费的上门诊断、方案讲解和效果复盘服务。' },
        ].map((item, i) => (
          <details class="faq-item reveal" open={i === 0}>
            <summary>{item.q}</summary>
            <p>{item.a}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container cta-content reveal">
      <span class="section-label">立即行动</span>
      <h2>让你的品牌出现在AI的推荐列表里</h2>
      <p>免费获取企业AI曝光现状诊断报告，看看你的品牌在AI搜索中的真实位置</p>
      <form class="cta-form" netlify name="lead" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="lead" />
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="您的姓名" required />
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="手机号码" required />
        <input type="text" name="industry" placeholder="所属行业" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">免费获取诊断</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }
  .hero-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .accent-dot { color: var(--accent); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 580px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .hero-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ===== Pain Points ===== */
  .pain-points { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .pain-grid .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .pain-grid .card svg { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pain-grid .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .pain-grid .card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== Core Services ===== */
  .core-services { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .services-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .service-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    min-width: 160px;
  }
  .service-icon { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .service-item p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* ===== Advantages ===== */
  .advantages { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .advantage-list { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .advantage-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .advantage-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .advantage-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .advantage-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .advantage-marker {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 0.65rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Trust ===== */
  .trust { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .case-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .case-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .case-cards .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .case-cards .card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .case-metric { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; }
  .metric-value { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; display: block; line-height: 1.2; }
  .metric-value .accent { color: var(--accent); }
  .metric-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .trust-action { text-align: center; }

  /* ===== FAQ ===== */
  .faq { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .faq-container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform var(--transition-smooth);
  }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: '−';
  }
  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .cta { background: var(--bg-primary); }
  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .cta-form input {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-smooth);
  }
  .cta-form input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .cta-form .btn { width: 100%; }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .case-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .services-row { gap: 0.5rem; }
    .service-item { min-width: 140px; }
  }
</style>
